author: cumminsh
msg: [ARIES-862] Remove usage of reactor pom as a parent pom, since we don't release the reactor poms with release by bundle (and therefore have an unwanted -SNAPSHOT dependency)

author: markt
msg: Various improvements to the DIGEST authenticator including <bug>52954</bug>, the disabling caching of an authenticated user in the session by default, tracking server rather than client nonces and better handling of stale nonce values.
This fixed CVE-2012-3439 Apache Tomcat DIGEST authentication weaknesses
